Author: basementbats
Text: When I used to restrict to like 400 on super strict keto and run 5 miles every day (and was underweight) if I binged I would scribble these giant sharpie marks all over my wrist so if I tried to pick up food I’d look at the sharpie and remember how upset I felt when I drew it on lol at that time I was like ‘I’m ok I don’t rlly have an ED I just like learning about them :-))))’
